Dear Rebecca Parem,
Greetings!
my name is Joy, and i am a 12 yr from america.
personally, i find you someone to look up to.
you are intelligent, funny, and altogether great!
you always find a way to make your fans smile.
you're that kind of animator that gives off unimaginable amounts of creativity and inspiration!
an ideal person to want to be.
not to mention, the originality! not to name names, but some animators just like to draw something related to a trend, or some fake story for views. (thank god that's not the majority, though.)
so, thank you for being someone to look up too when i don't have anyone here to do so.
with tons of laughs, Joy.
